==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Debit card
<hw>Deb"it card`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>debit</er>.]</ety> <def>a small usually plastic card with a magnetic
coded number, similar to a credit card, which is used to pay for
purchases by the electronic deduction of a sum of money (a debit)
directly from the card-holder's bank account. Such cards do not require
the establishment of a credit line, and such transactions do not incur
any interest payments.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Debitor</ent>⟦br⟧
